Mafia version 0.001005
======================

Mafia.pm is a Perl extension for easily moderating Mafia games.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

No modules outside Perl core are needed.

